_and_Testimonials\" >Utilising Social Proof and Testimonials<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-36\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#Benefits_of_Showcasing_Customer_Reviews_and_Case_Studies\" >Benefits of Showcasing Customer Reviews and Case Studies<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-37\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#Best_Practices_for_Integrating_Social_Proof_into_Your_Landing_Pages\" >Best Practices for Integrating Social Proof into Your Landing Pages<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-38\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#3_Measuring_Success_Key_Metrics_for_Landing_Page_Performance\" >3. Measuring Success: Key Metrics for Landing Page Performance<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-39\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#31_Conversion_Rate\" >3.1 Conversion Rate<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-40\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#32_Bounce_Rate\" >3.2 Bounce Rate<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-41\" href=\"https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/blog\/digital-marketing-agency\/landing-page-optimisation-how-to-convert-more-visitors-in-2025\/#33_Average_Tim